{"tid":1062981,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"淘寶集運集中討論區 (10) 1001記得開po","createTime":"2019-03-15T12:32:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-15T12:32:25.000Z","uid":43977,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"083368cba11fcd1af782d9ab1867a45c66f3fcea","tid":1062981,"uid":43977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T12:32:25.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>【唔好係隔離<ins>淘寶討論POST</ins>問集運】</strong></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>如果1001／太耐冇人覆而沉底，請自行開新</strong></span></span></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">人地答完問題可以<span style=\"color: gold;\">好評</span>以示感謝 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n巴絲見到識既問題幫下手答問題 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過都係請善用Google同爬文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </div><br />\n10）<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/852969/page/1   \" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/852969/page/1   </a><br />\n9) <a href=\"https://lih.kg/496866\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/496866</a><br />\n8) <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/480102\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/480102</a><br />\n7) <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/470997\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/470997</a><br />\n6) <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/360861\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/360861</a><br />\n5) <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/269393\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/269393</a><br />\n4) <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/203596\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/203596</a><br />\n3) <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/141543\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/141543</a><br />\n2) <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/80004\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/80004</a><br />\n1) <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/14609\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/14609</a><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>【常用推介】</strong></span></span></div><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">【問】<strong>邊間集運好用？有無推介？</strong><br />\n【答】<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>各有各好，自行 Google</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>集運有伏齊齊Share</strong></span><br />\n <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">【等巴絲打唔洗中伏】</span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好用留住自己用，唔需要開名推介<span style=\"color: red;\">*</span>（見#3）</span></strong> <br />\n <strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">【除非你想燈死多幾間，以後唔洗用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />】</span></strong></span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">*</span>  官集／上左神枱係人都知果堆例外</strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">【集運FAQ】</div></span><br />\n【問】睇中10樣野，10樣都唔同鋪，如果逐樣運黎香港，運費好貴，點算？<br />\n【答】<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>有樣野叫「集運」</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【問】其實一般集運係點樣運作？<br />\n【答】<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">1）國內段</span></strong><br />\n買左幾樣野＞各自寄去集運公司<strong>國內集運倉</strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">2）中國至香港段</span></strong><br />\n通知集運公司打包寄香港＞<strong>剩係俾寄香港運費</strong>＞香港拎貨<br />\n（幾件貨集埋一齊運慳運費）<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">*</span> 詳見#2 / Google</strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【問】咩係「官集」？咩係「私集」？<br />\n【答】<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">「官集」（順豐*／中通／4PX）：淘寶認證嘅幾間集運公司</span></strong><br />\n # 價格及介紹：<a href=\"https://goo.gl/dgwcuL\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FdgwcuL&d=1zr6t4yB9inWhfXylFPsafDXWQKahOldmH8%2Bpia8yKE%3D&h=721d40fb\" target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/dgwcuL</a><br />\n # 時效保障（超時罰款）：<a href=\"https://goo.gl/pxX3aE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FpxX3aE&d=1zr6t4yB9inWhfXylFPsafDXWQKahOldmH8%2Bpia8yKE%3D&h=5844c3b9\" target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/pxX3aE</a><br />\n # 落單、集運、俾錢全部野係哂淘寶APP／網頁版內做哂<br />\n # 較易使用／較多限制，可寄物品較少／有一定好處 <br />\n <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">*</span> 順豐自2017年7月1日起會計算體積重</strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">「私集」：私人開嘅集運公司</span></strong><br />\n # 要自行搵集運公司開A/C、認領貨物、集運、俾錢<br />\n # Google/淘寶搵&quot;集運&quot;會搵到一堆<br />\n # 較少限制／價格較親民<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n【問】淘寶結賬果陣點揀用邊個自提點？<br />\n【答】<br />\n結賬果陣<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>只係揀用邊間官集，件貨到左集運倉先再揀 1.送貨地址 / 2.自提點地址</strong></span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">*</span> 唔同公司嘅自提點唔同，賣家寄出左就無得改。<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">*</span>  用<span style=\"color: blue;\">順豐智能櫃</span>收件就要揀【順豐】，想去郵局就要揀【中通】。<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">*</span>  如你揀左【中通】，到左集運倉之後係無得揀<span style=\"color: blue;\">順豐智能櫃</span>收件。</strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【問】官集唔俾運＿＿，點算好？<br />\n【答】<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>有樣野叫「私集」</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【問】邊間運得＿＿嗎？<br />\n【答】<span style=\"color: red;\">你應該問邊間唔得（誠實的孩子除外）</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【問】集運壞處？？<br />\n【答】<br />\n1）最好就唔好運易腐食物，<span style=\"color: red;\">擺係集運倉驚變壞 🦀</span><br />\n2）有啲集運公司會偷野、容易遺失，<span style=\"color: red;\">出左事未必有人負責（無人賠／跟進）</span><br />\n3）某啲淘寶賣家唔會寫你個名，<span style=\"color: red;\">去到集運倉無人認領，咁你份野就byebye</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【問】淘寶顯示已簽收，但集運倉仲未見到<br />\n【答】入庫需時／假簽收<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">*</span> 雙11等大型活動期間，假簽收會多啲／入庫會慢啲，等下</strong><br />\n太耐嘅話可以<strong>旺旺賣家幫手問下速遞</strong>／<strong>聯絡集運有無收過</strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【問】國內段物流停左好多日無更新點好？例：停留上海中轉站成個星期<br />\n【答】<br />\n1) 叫賣家幫手問下<br />\n2) 搵速遞客服催下<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">*</span> 雙11等大型活動期間，物流會慢啲，俾啲耐性等下先</strong><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">【其他】</div></span><br />\n【問】學生哥冇信用卡點好？<br />\n【答】<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">PPS</span>：去OK便利店整，唔洗錢，有提款卡就得 <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">八達通</span>：只for an機，ios未有<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">支付寶HK</span>：<a href=\"https://www.alipay.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.alipay.hk&d=1zr6t4yB9inWhfXylFPsafDXWQKahOldmH8%2Bpia8yKE%3D&h=3bd35250\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.alipay.hk</a><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">「拍住賞」卡</span>：當Mastercard用，便利店直接買<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">請打擊代充，此post禁止打手及討論任何代充</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">Template: <a href=\"https://github.com/lihkgtb/lihkgtb/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgithub.com%2Flihkgtb%2Flihkgtb%2F&d=1zr6t4yB9inWhfXylFPsafDXWQKahOldmH8%2Bpia8yKE%3D&h=69a3e14a\" target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/lihkgtb/lihkgtb/</a></span>"}]}